  "text": "Using DDA code [CITATION_1] we have calculated the extinction factors of the CO ice stretching mode considering other shapes: (1) ellipsoids with an axis ratio of 5; (2) the so-called irregular shape DW1996; (3) some aggregates randomly generated with spheres of a radius monomer of 0.17 µm. The particle labeled DW1996 consists of an assemblage of 13 cubic units [CITATION_2] , and we have selected this non-realistic shape only for testing the results with different irregular shapes.",
